name.label: Eolas Prints PETG: Certified UV Resistant

metadata.adhesion_info: Adhesive like magigoo recommended 1 This PETG filament is engineered with certified UV resistance, making it a great choice for long-lasting prints. It is designed to withstand long-term exposure to sunlight, ensuring it will not discolor or degrade in the outdoors. Perfect for outdoor 3D printing.
